  "signal_description": "This SIGNAL query calculates the duration of issues that were rejected or marked as 'Won't Do'. It groups the issues by the month when they were rejected and orders the results by the month. The query retrieves the first end time of the 'Change Status to Closed' event and subtracts it from the first end time of the 'Change Status to In Progress' event. The duration is filtered to include only events where the event name matches the pattern 'Change Status to In Progress' followed by 'Change Status to Closed' and the 'ResolutionStatus' column is either 'Rejected' or 'Won't Do'. The query is executed on the 'defaultview-217' table."
